					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Scripts are files that contain [[SmaCC Transformation Toolkit rewrite rules]], [[SmaCC Transformation Toolkit methods]], [[SmaCC Transformation Toolkit properties]], or imports of other script files. When AST nodes are processed by the script, the rules are applied in the order in which they appear in the script."
